data.title: Israel announces timeline for implementing first phase of peace plan
data.text:
Israel announces timeline for implementing first phase of peace plan

NewsFeed Israel announces timeline for implementing first phase of peace plan

A government spokesperson has laid out how Israel will implement the first phase of US President Donald Trump’s peace plan in Gaza, saying it will start after today’s Israeli government cabinet meeting.
